OOC: Sorry, I never intended to let this guy fall out of circulation 
like I did - between having unpredictable working hours and the 
world's worst Internet connection, things have slid outta control for 
me lately.

Jackie paces about the base, looking for something to do.  Seeing the 
control room unoccupied, he decides to keep an optic on the scanner 
readouts while he's busy taking up space.  The white and grey bot 
plunks himself into the most convenient chair, puts his feet up, and 
turns on his internal music player - Rob Zombie at a volume level high 
enough to be heard plainly throughout the base.
